body:
h1. This is the data for my blog

It is automatically transformed by "Jekyll":http://github.com/mojombo/jekyll into a static site whenever I push this repository to GitHub.

h1. License

The following directories and their contents are Copyright Lance Hunt. You may not reuse anything therein without my permission:

* _posts/
* images/

All other directories and files are MIT Licensed. Feel free to use the HTML and CSS as you please. If you do use them, a link back to http://github.com/mojombo/jekyll would be appreciated, but is not required.

h1. Attribution

This site is my clone of Tom Preson-Warner's github blogging approach from https://github.com/mojombo/mojombo.github.com
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
